WEBVTT

00:13:59.389 --> 00:14:04.485
the despair that authoritarian
politicians prey upon

00:14:04.509 --> 00:14:06.874
if our systems stay rigged.

00:14:08.900 --> 00:14:14.351
I called Ravi before coming here
to ask permission to share his story.

00:14:15.370 --> 00:14:18.164
I asked if there was any message
he wanted to give people.

00:14:19.566 --> 00:14:22.050
He said, "[Gujarati]."

00:14:23.193 --> 00:14:24.343
Wake up.

00:14:26.101 --> 00:14:28.475
"[Gujarati]."

00:14:28.499 --> 00:14:29.689
Don't be afraid.